            "title": "kW vs kWh: The Most Important Constants in Solar Storage",
            "description": "Confusing Power (kW) with Energy (kWh) is the #1 mistake homeowners make when buying batteries. Here is the definitive engineering explanation with examples.",
            "updated": "2026-02-18",
