            "title": "Canada Solar Battery Market 2026: Cost, Provincial Incentives & ROI",
            "description": "Complete guide to Canadian residential battery storage in 2026. Hardware costs, installation pricing, provincial rebates, and ROI assessment by region.",
            "updated": "2026-02-18",
